', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/6124/', '', 'Opium, Dextropropoxyphene, Naloxone, Naltrexone', 'Rimegepant, Eptinezumab, Ubrogepant, Galcanezumab, Atogepant, Methysergide, Erenumab, Fremanezumab, Tinidazole, Ascorbic acid, Hydroflumethiazide, More', 1767369485);
